column2: SELECT TOP #  p.objid,p.petroMag_u,p.petroMag_g,p.petroMag_r,p.petroMag_i,p.petroMag_z,   s.class, s.z as redshift FROM photoObj AS p  JOIN specObj s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid WHERE   s.class = &&&  AND s.z < #  AND s.z > #  AND p.petroMag_u > #  AND p.petroMag_g > #  AND p.petroMag_r > #  AND p.petroMag_i > #  AND p.petroMag_z > #
